description:
Joe Rainey performing at Radio Heartland's Minnesota Music Month showcase
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube

Pow wow singer Joe Rainey performed at Radio Heartland's Minnesota Music Month showcase back in April, alongside Alan Sparhawk Solo Band, Maygen & The Birdwatcher, and Kelley Smith.

Watch Joe Rainey's full performance above.
